  "text": "Methanol was measured by a commercially available protontransfer-reaction mass spectrometer (PTR-MS, Ionicon Analytik GmbH, Innsbruck, A). The instrument and its operating mode had been described in detail by [CITATION_1] . Here we describe the experimental setup from the gas inlet to the instrument and go then into specifics of the PTR-MS used in this field study.",
